<tr id="L305"><td><a href="#L305">305</a></td><td>K'MPEC:  The Empire will not be destroyed for one family's honour.</td></tr>

<tr id="L306"><td><a href="#L306">306</a></td><td>PICARD:  Unacceptable, K'mpec.</td></tr>

<tr id="L307"><td><a href="#L307">307</a></td><td>DURAS:  You have no say in this, cha'DIch!</td></tr>

<tr id="L308"><td><a href="#L308">308</a></td><td>PICARD:  I speak now as the Captain of the USS Enterprise and Lieutenant Worf's commanding officer. You will not execute a member of my crew, nor will I turn his brother over to you.</td></tr>

<tr id="L309"><td><a href="#L309">309</a></td><td>K'MPEC:  This is not the Federation, Picard. If you defy an order of the High Council, the alliance with the Federation could fall to dust.</td></tr>

<tr id="L310"><td><a href="#L310">310</a></td><td>PICARD:  The alliance with the Federation is not based on lies, K'mpec! Protect your secrets if you must, but you will not sacrifice these men.</td></tr>

<tr id="L311"><td><a href="#L311">311</a></td><td>WORF:  I will die for the Empire.</td></tr>

<tr id="L312"><td><a href="#L312">312</a></td><td>PICARD:  Lieutenant.</td></tr>

<tr id="L313"><td><a href="#L313">313</a></td><td>WORF:  The cha'DIch will be silent. Allow my brother to return to his life. Only you need know his true bloodline.</td></tr>

<tr id="L314"><td><a href="#L314">314</a></td><td>DURAS:  Not acceptable. His honour would demand revenge.</td></tr>

<tr id="L315"><td><a href="#L315">315</a></td><td>WORF:  If you allow him to live, I will give you something that will serve your purpose far more than my death. I will accept discommendation.</td></tr>

<tr id="L316"><td><a href="#L316">316</a></td><td>DURAS:  You would do this in open council?</td></tr>

<tr id="L317"><td><a href="#L317">317</a></td><td>K'MPEC:  It would be the same as admitting your father's guilt, Worf.</td></tr>

<tr id="L318"><td><a href="#L318">318</a></td><td>WORF:  So be it.</td></tr>

<tr id="L319"><td><a href="#L319">319</a></td><td>K'MPEC:  Your heart is Klingon. It will be done. What has been said here will never be spoken of again.</td></tr>

<tr id="L320"><td><a href="#L320">320</a></td><td>WORF:  You are the son of a traitor.</td></tr>

<tr id="L321"><td><a href="#L321">321</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: Worf slaps Duras' face</td></tr>

